1. *Telo* je naša najvažnija škola. (The body is our most important school.)

2. Ona voli da pokazuje svoje *telo*. (She loves to show off her body.)

3. Učenici su se radovali kada je učiteljica postavila *telesne* vežbe. (The students were delighted when the teacher set physical exercises.)

4. Početak je uvijek u *telu*. (The beginning is always in the body.)

5. Ona je našla mir u *težini* svog tela. (She found peace in the weight of her body.)